    <!-- Welcome / First Launch -->
    <string name="welcome_title">Barka da zuwa</string>
    <string name="welcome_sovereignty">Maɓallanku.\nKuɗaɗenku.\nIkon mallakarku.</string>
    <string name="welcome_desc">Ba a adana kuɗaɗenka a wannan app ɗin ba. Suna kan blockchain, ƙarƙashin ikon maɓallanka masu zaman kansu.\n\nWannan app ɗin yana adana maɓallanka cikin tsaro kawai. Ba za mu iya samun kuɗaɗenka ba.\n\nLura: Wasu token (USDC, USDT) masu bayarwa na iya daskarewa. Don mafi girman ikon mallaka, yi amfani da ETH na asali ko token marasa iko.</string>
    <string name="welcome_warning_title">Maɓallanka = Kuɗaɗenka</string>
    <string name="welcome_warning_desc">Idan ka rasa maɓallanka masu zaman kansu ko ka raba su da wani, za ka rasa ikon kuɗaɗenka har abada.\n\nBabu zaɓin dawowa. Babu ƙungiyar taimako da za su iya taimaka maka. Wannan shine yanayin mallaka na gaskiya.\n\nKullum ajiye kwafin tsaro na maɓallanka.</string>
    <string name="welcome_opensource">Software mai buɗewa. Tabbatar, kar ka amince kawai.</string>
    <string name="welcome_start">Na fahimta, mu fara</string>

